des:
A series of daily inspirational quotes, phrases, and messages, or sayings from Anthony Ware, Principal and Founder of AWare Catalysts. Listen to Anthony talk about Culture, Travel, Empathy, Self-Awareness, Running, Patience, Mental Health, Startups, and more. There's a ton of good happening in the world. Time to make it louder :)

This Flash Briefing skill may contain profanity. It’s not a kids show. Anthony is passionate about making positivity louder. If you choose not to listen, great! If you do, great! ;)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
